To gain the rank of a 'wizard' you need to pass this test.
You can use your own coding from your areas.

1. Do an object that is needed in a quest. The object must not
   be a weapon or an armour and it has to contain short and long
   descs, weight and it must be gettable. (You must have a quest done.)

2. Code one secret passage between two rooms. (no using of add_exit())

3. Make one monster which is able to cast spells and uses some
   special feature.

4. Write a description of about 50 words of a forest room and
   some item.

